conversation.message: Hi, my name is Alex and I'm reaching out from DeepData AI. We're a data processing solution that helps companies like yours streamline their data operations and gain deeper insights. Can you tell me a little bit about your current data processing setup?

conversation.message: (skeptical) Oh, another data processing solution. We already have a few vendors we're working with, and to be honest, I'm not sure we're in the market for another one. What makes DeepData AI so special?

conversation.speaker: Seller
conversation.message: I completely understand your skepticism. However, our AI-powered solution can handle large volumes of data much faster and more accurately than traditional methods. We've seen companies reduce their data processing time by up to 70%. I'd love to show you a demo to see if it could be a good fit for your organization.

conversation.speaker: Buyer
conversation.message: (objection) That sounds interesting, but we're in the middle of a major project right now, and I'm not sure we have the bandwidth to take on something new. Plus, I'm not convinced that your solution is worth the cost. What's the pricing looking like?

conversation.speaker: Seller
conversation.message: Our pricing is competitive, and we offer customized plans based on the specific needs of each company. For a company of your size, it would likely be in the range of $10,000 to $20,000 per year. However, I'd like to emphasize that our solution can help you save money in the long run by reducing manual labor and increasing efficiency.

conversation.speaker: Buyer
conversation.message: (firmly) I appreciate the pitch, but to be honest, we're just not interested in exploring new data processing solutions at this time. We've got our hands full with our current project, and I don't see this as a priority for us. Maybe send me an email with some more information, and I'll take a look when I have some more time.

conversation.speaker: Seller
conversation.message: I completely understand, and I'll make sure to send you that information. However, I want to make sure you're aware that we're offering a limited-time discount for new customers, and it might be worth considering before we fill up our pipeline.

conversation.speaker: Buyer
conversation.message: (definitively) Alex, I appreciate the follow-up, but like I said, we're just not interested right now. Please don't send any more emails or make any more calls. We're not going to be moving forward with DeepData AI.
